media:group.media:title: Jerma Rumble - Live Action!
media:group.media:description:
It's been a long time coming, but here is the latest from the Jerma Wrestling Federation.
A lot of people made this possible, but a very special thanks to:
Co-Producer: Ray Fuschetti 1st Camera: Dusty Wood Script Supervisor: Kevin Harrington Makeup: David Manning Music: Shaun McGlinn http://www.youtube.com/blordow Additional Editing: Dan Earle and especially to Tim Stanton for letting us act like assholes in his Ring
So, here is the part where I say thank you to YOU watching this video. This was something I've wanted to do for over a year now, and without people that give a shit like you guys, I never would have been able to do it. Thank you for sticking with this channel for all these years, and I hope ya stick around for some more.
